ers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/hadith-khtubah-al-hajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18133,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah al-Hajah: How the Prophet began his sermons","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave us the combination of all good things and their endings, for he taught us the statements of prayer and the statements of need. The statements of prayer are, \u201cAll greetings, prayers, and good things are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37220,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/25\/ibn-abbas-following-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":18133,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Quran: Following Quran protects from misguidance, damnation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ikramah reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah has guaranteed for one who follows the Quran that he will not be led astray in the world, nor be damned in the Hereafter.\u201d Then, he recited the verse, \u201cThus, whoever follows My guidance will not be led\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/05\/follow-sunnah-beware-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18133,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Follow the Prophet, beware of innovation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Irbad ibn Sariyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prayed with us one day. Then, he faced us and delivered an eloquent sermon that brought tears to our eyes and hearts were shaken by it. It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, it is as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/19\/left-you-with-kitab-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18133,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: I have left you with the Book, the Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have left you with two matters which will never lead you astray, as long as you hold to them: the Book of Allah and the Sunnah of his Prophet.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 1661 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text